title: 12/01/20 DPS-BEST OF
itunes:title: 12/01/20 DPS-BEST OF
description:
On Today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show , DP Recaps last night's MNF matchup between the Seahawks and Eagles. Should the comments made towards DK Metcalf by Jim Schwartz have been taken personal? Why didn't we see more Jalen Hurts? We're joined by former Eagles QB Ron Jaworski, Senior Writer covering the Ravens Jeff Zrebiac and Pro Football Talk's Mike Florio. Plus, we discuss Michael Buble popularity boost during the Holiday season
